OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FConditions at an immigration detention
OL,7,Fcentre have been branded the "worst"
OL,8,Fin the country by a watchdog who
OL,9,Fdescribed the "chaos" he discovered
OL,10,Fthere "truly shocking".
OL,12,FChief inspector of prisons Charlie
OL,13,FTaylor said he was so concerned by
OL,14,Fwhat he found at Harmondsworth
OL,15,Fimmigration removal centre (IRC) that
OL,16,Fhe raised his concerns with the then
OL,17,Fhome secretary, who never replied.
