OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FViolence and drug use was rife at the
OL,7,Fsite near Heathrow Airport in west
OL,8,FLondon, having "substantially
OL,9,Fincreased" since inspectors last
OL,10,Fvisited.
OL,12,FThere had also been several serious
OL,13,Fsuicide attempts at the "decrepit"
OL,14,Fbuilding which can hold close to 700
OL,15,Fmen, according to findings published
OL,16,Fon Tuesday.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@JO]uD@YOUuD@bO]
