OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FThe number of assaults had doubled
OL,7,Fsince the last inspection and drug-
OL,8,Ftaking, which is typically rare in
OL,9,Fimmigration removal centres, was
OL,10,F"widespread".
OL,12,FInspectors "could smell cannabis and
OL,13,Fsaw detainees openly smoking in
OL,14,Fcommunal areas without being
OL,15,Fchallenged by staff who largely kept
OL,16,Fto offices with 'do not enter' taped
OL,17,Facross their doors", the watchdog
OL,18,Fwarned.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]tD@LOUyD@SO]
