OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "The level of chaos
OL,7,Fthat we found at Harmondsworth was
OL,8,Ftruly shocking and we left deeply
OL,9,Fconcerned that some of those held
OL,10,Fthere were at imminent risk of harm.
OL,12,F"Nobody should be detained in an
OL,13,Fimmigration removal centre unless they
OL,14,Fare going to be removed quickly from
OL,15,Fthe country, yet around 60% of
OL,16,Fdetainees were released from the
OL,17,Fcentre, with only a third deported,
OL,18,Fwhich begs the question of why so much
OL,19,Ftaxpayer money was being spent keeping
OL,20,Fthem locked up in the first place."
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOU|D@cO]
