OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FMr Taylor wrote to former home
OL,7,Fsecretary James Cleverly on March 12
OL,8,Fafter the inspection between February
OL,9,F12`29 "setting out the many failures
OL,10,Fat the centre" but has "received no
OL,11,Fresponse", according to the watchdog,
OL,13,FWhile the new director had a "good
OL,14,Funderstanding" of many of the
OL,15,Fchallenges faced by the centre and was
OL,16,F"beginning to make good progress" in
OL,17,Fimproving conditions, she will "need
OL,18,Fstrong and consistent support at every
OL,19,Flevel to succeed", Mr Taylor added.
