OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FThe watchdog told how cells had been
OL,7,Fdoubled up to hold more men but if
OL,8,Fdetainees refused to share, they were
OL,9,Fheld in a separation unit until they
OL,10,Fagreed.
OL,12,FMitie Care and Custody, which runs the
OL,13,Fcentre, faced numerous challenges
OL,14,Fincluding staff shortages and a
OL,15,F"shambolic retendering process" led by
OL,16,Fthe Home Office meant that leaders had
OL,17,F"no idea whether they would still be
OL,18,Frunning the centre in the next few
OL,19,Fmonths", according to the findings.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@_O]yD@AOU{D@GO]
