OL,6,FThe contractual uncertainties had been
OL,7,Fa problem since last year which made
OL,8,Fit "all but impossible to recruit
OL,9,Fpermanent senior staff, who might only
OL,10,Fbe in post for a matter of weeks", the
OL,11,Fwatchdog said.
