OL,3,CWatchdog blasts 'worst' immigration
OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FKolbassia Haoussou, a refugee who fled
OL,7,Ftorture in Africa and now works for
OL,8,Fcharity Freedom from Torture, said he
OL,9,Fwas held in Harmondsworth when he
OL,10,Ffirst arrived in the UK in 2005 and
OL,11,Fknows "only too well how profoundly
OL,12,Fdamaging detention can be" as he
OL,13,Fcalled on the new Government to
OL,14,F"rebuild a just asylum system that
OL,15,Frespects human dignity and the rule of
OL,16,Flaw".
