OL,6,FA statement from Mitie said the
OL,7,Fcompany acknowledged that the
OL,8,Fconditions and standard of care "fell
OL,9,Fbelow the level we would expect at
OL,10,Fthis facility" when the inspection
OL,11,Ftook place.
OL,13,F"We take on board all of the
OL,14,Frecommendations that they have made
OL,15,Fand will work tirelessly to implement
OL,16,Fthem as soon as reasonably
OL,17,Fpracticable."
