OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,FThe statement said conditions at the
OL,7,Ftime had been affected by factors
OL,8,Fincluding "an interim increase in room
OL,9,Foccupancy rates, due to restricted
OL,10,Fcapacity at the IRC, with one wing
OL,11,F(out of four) being closed for
OL,12,Frefurbishment".
OL,14,FThe statement added: "This work is
OL,15,Fscheduled to be completed in August,
OL,16,Ffollowing which a second wing (the
OL,17,Fconditions of which were particularly
OL,18,Fcriticised by the inspection) will
OL,19,Fitself be closed for refurbishment."
