OL,6,FMitie added: "The demographic of the
OL,7,Fpopulation at the IRC has changed
OL,8,Fsignificantly over the past 24 months,
OL,9,Fwith Time Served Foreign National
OL,10,FOffenders (TSFNOs) now representing
OL,11,Fbetween 50 and 60% of the total IRC
OL,12,Fpopulation at any time. 53% of all
OL,13,Fresidents now arrive from police
OL,14,Fcustody or prisons, up from 31% in
OL,15,F2022.
OL,26,@nD@NOU
