OL,6,F"The change in demographics has led to
OL,7,Fa material increase in disruptive
OL,8,Fbehaviours and incidents: between June
OL,9,Fand November 2023, there were 97
OL,10,Ffights and incidents of violence, up
OL,11,Ffrom 26 incidents during same period
OL,12,Fthe previous year, all of which
OL,13,Finvolved TSFNOs.
