OL,4,Cdetention centre conditions
OL,6,F"In response to this change in
OL,7,Fdemographics, we agreed a new staffing
OL,8,Fmodel with the Home Office (with
OL,9,Fimproved pay and contracted hours for
OL,10,Fall Detention & Custody Officers
OL,11,F(DCOs)), which has led to an 40%
OL,12,Fincrease in the number of DCOs
OL,13,Fdeployed at the IRC, with further DCOs
OL,14,Fstill being recruited."
OL,16,FThis had led to "a material
OL,17,Fimprovement" in staff engagement and
OL,18,Fretention, the statement said.
