OL,6,FMitie said it was enforcing a smoking
OL,7,Fban introduced by the Home Office last
OL,8,Fmonth across all IRCs.
OL,10,FThe Home Office said: "We take the
OL,11,Fwelfare and safety of people in our
OL,12,Fcare very seriously and it is vital
OL,13,Fthat detention and removals are
OL,14,Fcarried out with dignity and respect.
OL,16,F"The number of custody officers and
OL,17,Fdedicated welfare staff at
OL,18,FHarmondsworth IRC has been increased
OL,19,Fsince the inspection."
